        public Type[] getVariadicParameterTypesFor(int numArgs)
        Gets the variadic signature of this method for an invocation with a given number of arguments. This operation duplicates the last formal parameter as necessary such that the number of parameters equals the number of arguments this method was invoked with.
        Parameters:
